# --- Locations ---

noria:Site_DC_Paris a bot:Site ;
    rdfs:label "Paris Data Center"@en, "Centre de Données de Paris"@fr ;
    rdfs:comment "Primary data center for core business applications and infrastructure, providing high availability and disaster recovery capabilities."@en ;
